### ต้องติดตั้ง VSCode extension "REST Client" (humao.rest-client) ก่อน
### จากนั้นจะเห็นลิงก์ "Send Request" ปรากฏเหนือ request แต่ละอัน กดเพื่อยิงได้เลย
### แอปต้องรันอยู่ที่ http://localhost:8080 (./mvnw spring-boot:run)

@host = http://localhost:8080

### Health check
GET {{host}}/actuator/health


### =========================
### Users API (in-memory)
### =========================

### GET /users - list all
GET {{host}}/users


### GET /users/{id} - get one (มีอยู่แล้วตั้งแต่ seed)
GET {{host}}/users/1


### GET /users/{id} - not found (expect 404)
GET {{host}}/users/999


### POST /users - create (expect 201)
POST {{host}}/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Patricia Lebsack",
  "username": "Karianne",
  "email": "Julianne.OConner@kory.org",
  "phone": "493-170-9623 x156",
  "website": "kale.biz"
}


### POST /users - validation error (expect 400 + messages)
POST {{host}}/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "phone": "123"
}

### PUT /users/{id} - update existing (expect 200)
PUT {{host}}/users/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Leanne G. (updated)",
  "username": "Bret",
  "email": "leanne@example.com"
}


### PUT /users/{id} - not found (expect 404)
PUT {{host}}/users/999
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Nobody",
  "username": "nobody",
  "email": "nobody@example.com"
}


### DELETE /users/{id} - delete (expect 204)
DELETE {{host}}/users/3


### DELETE /users/{id} - not found on second delete (expect 404)
DELETE {{host}}/users/3


### =========================
### Items API (H2/Postgres)
### =========================

### GET /api/items - list all
GET {{host}}/api/items


### POST /api/items - create (expect 201)
POST {{host}}/api/items
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "coffee"
}


### GET /api/items/{id}
GET {{host}}/api/items/1


### DELETE /api/items/{id} - delete (expect 204)
DELETE {{host}}/api/items/1
